    <summaries>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2008-07-08</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2008-08-13T18:21:25Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Oil Price Reduction Act of 2008 - Prohibits U.S. bilateral assistance and arms exports (not including humanitarian assistance) to any country that is a major net oil exporter, including any country that is a member of the Organization of Petroleum Exporting Countries (OPEC), if such country is engaged in oil price fixing to the detriment of the U.S. economy.</p><p>Amends the Internal Revenue Code to allow taxpayers who drive a highway vehicle fueled by gasoline or diesel fuel a $1,000 tax credit in 2008.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
    <title>Oil Price Reduction Act of 2008</title>
