      </item>
      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To combat international oil price fixing and to amend the Internal Revenue Code of 1986 to allow individuals a credit against income tax of at least $1,000 to offset high 2008 gasoline and diesel fuel prices.</title>
      </item>
